ActPublic Service Employment Act
SubjectAppointment or Deployment of Alternates Exclusion Approval Order
PrecisOrder making the NEW APPOINTMENT OR DEPLOYMENT OF ALTERNATES EXCLUSION APPROVAL ORDER in order to add the new section 39.1 of the Public Service Employment Act to the list of provisions from which the appointments and deployments of alternates are excluded.
